## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="7f284-102">名为 `xsi:choice` 的 XML 架构元素定义用于定义一个复杂元素，该元素在实例中只能包含一个子元素（maxoccurs = 1）。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7f284-102">The XML schema element definition named `xsi:choice` is used to define a complex element that can contain only one child in an instance (maxoccurs = 1).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7f284-103">该子元素可以是几种类型之一，并且可以有多个名称之一。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7f284-103">That child can be one of several types, and it can have one of several names.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7f284-104">每个名称与特定类型相关联;但是，多个名称可以与相同类型相关联。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7f284-104">Each name is associated with a specific type; however, several names can be associated with the same type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7f284-105">因此，此类元素的实例是 indistinct 的。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7f284-105">Because of this, an instance of such an element is indistinct.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7f284-106">例如，请考虑下面的架构片段，它定义了一个名为 `MyChoice`的 indistinct 元素。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7f284-106">For example, consider the following schema fragment that defines such an indistinct element named `MyChoice`.</span></span>  
  
```  
<xsd:complexType name="MyChoice">  
 <xsd:sequence>  
 <xsd:choice minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="1">  
 <xsd:element minOccurs="1" maxOccurs="1" name="ChoiceOne" type="xsd:string" />  
 <xsd:element minOccurs="1" maxOccurs="1" name="ChoiceTwo" type="xsd:string" />  
 </xsd:choice>  
 </xsd:sequence>  
</xsd:complexType>  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7f284-107"><xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlChoiceIdentifierAttribute> 允许您为成员的每个实例分配特殊的枚举值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7f284-107">The <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlChoiceIdentifierAttribute> allows you to assign a special enumeration value to each instance of the member.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7f284-108">您必须自行创建枚举，或者可以通过[XML 架构定义工具（xsd.exe）](/dotnet/standard/serialization/xml-schema-definition-tool-xsd-exe)生成它。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7f284-108">You must either create the enumeration yourself or it can be generated by the [XML Schema Definition Tool (Xsd.exe)](/dotnet/standard/serialization/xml-schema-definition-tool-xsd-exe).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7f284-109">下面C#的代码演示如何将 <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlChoiceIdentifierAttribute> 应用到 `Item` 字段;<xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlChoiceIdentifierAttribute.MemberName%2A> 属性标识包含用于检测选择的枚举的字段。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7f284-109">The following C# code shows how the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlChoiceIdentifierAttribute> is applied to an `Item` field; the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlChoiceIdentifierAttribute.MemberName%2A> property identifies the field that contains the enumeration that is further used to detect the choice.</span></span>  
  
```  
public class Choices{  
 [XmlChoiceIdentifier("ItemType")]  
 [XmlChoiceIdentifier("ChoiceOne")]  
 [XmlChoiceIdentifier("ChoiceTwo")]  
 public string MyChoice;  
  
 // Do not serialize this next field:  
 [XmlIgnore]  
 public ItemChoiceType ItemType;  
}  
// Do not include this enumeration in the XML schema.  
[XmlType(IncludeInSchema = false)]  
public enum ItemChoiceType{  
 ChoiceOne,  
 ChoiceTwo,  
}  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7f284-110">当该代码准备就绪时，可以通过将 `ItemType` 字段设置为相应的枚举来序列化和反序列化此类。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7f284-110">When this code is in place, you can serialize and deserialize this class by setting the `ItemType` field to an appropriate enumeration.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7f284-111">例如，若要序列化 `Choice` 类， C#代码如下所示。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7f284-111">For example, to serialize the `Choice` class, the C# code resembles the following.</span></span>  
  
```  
Choices mc = new Choices();  
mc.MyChoice = "Item Choice One";  
mc.ItemType = ItemChoiceType.ChoiceOne;  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7f284-112">反序列化时C# ，代码如下所示：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7f284-112">When deserializing, the C# code resembles the following:</span></span>  
  
```  
MyChoice mc = (MyChoice) myXmlSerializer.Deserialize(myReader);  
if(mc.ItemType == ItemChoiceType.ChoiceOne)  
 {  
     // Handle choice one.  
 }  
if(mc.ItemType == ItemChoiceType.ChoiceTwo)  
 {  
     // Handle choice two.  
 }  
if(mc.ItemType != null)  
 {  
     throw CreateUnknownTypeException(mc.Item);  
 }  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7f284-113">使用 <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlChoiceIdentifierAttribute> 时，还有第二种情况。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7f284-113">There is a second scenario when the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlChoiceIdentifierAttribute> is used.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7f284-114">在下面的架构中，成员是返回项（maxOccurs = "未绑定"）的数组的字段。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7f284-114">In the following schema, the member is a field that returns an array of items (maxOccurs="unbounded").</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7f284-115">该数组可以包含首选项（"MoreData"）和第二个选项（""）的对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7f284-115">The array can contain objects of the first choice ("D-a-t-a"), and of the second choice ("MoreData").</span></span>  
  
```  
<xsd:complexType name="MyChoice">  
 <xsd:sequence>  
 <xsd:choice minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="unbounded">  
 <xsd:element minOccurs="1" maxOccurs="1" name="D-a-t-a" type="xsd:string" />  
 <xsd:element minOccurs="1" maxOccurs="1" name="MoreData" type="xsd:string" />  
 </xsd:choice>  
 </xsd:sequence>  
</xsd:complexType>  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7f284-116">然后，生成的类使用字段返回项的数组。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7f284-116">The resulting class then uses a field to return an array of items.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7f284-117">对于数组中的每个项，还必须找到相应的 `ItemChoiceType` 枚举。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7f284-117">For each item in the array, a corresponding `ItemChoiceType` enumeration must also be found.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7f284-118">匹配枚举包含在 `ItemsElementName` 字段返回的数组中。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7f284-118">The matching enumerations are contained in the array returned by the `ItemsElementName` field.</span></span>  
  
```  
public class MyChoice {  
 [System.Xml.Serialization.XmlElementAttribute("D-a-t-a", typeof(string), IsNullable=false)]  
 [System.Xml.Serialization.XmlElementAttribute("MoreData", typeof(string), IsNullable=false)]  
 [System.Xml.Serialization.XmlChoiceIdentifierAttribute("ItemsElementName")]  
 public string[] Items;  
 [System.Xml.Serialization.XmlElementAttribute(IsNullable=false)]  
 [System.Xml.Serialization.XmlIgnoreAttribute()]  
 public ItemsChoiceType[] ItemsElementName;  
}  
[System.Xml.Serialization.XmlTypeAttribute(IncludeInSchema=false)]  
public enum ItemsChoiceType {  
 [System.Xml.Serialization.XmlEnumAttribute("D-a-t-a")]  
 Data,  
 MoreData,  
}  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7f284-119">反序列化包含一系列选项的对象时，请使用控件结构（如 if .。。then .。。else 结构）来确定如何对特定值进行反序列化。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7f284-119">When deserializing an object that includes a range of choices, use a control structure (such as an if...then...else structure) to determine how to deserialize a particular value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7f284-120">在控件结构中，检查枚举值并相应地反序列化值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7f284-120">In the control structure, check the enumeration value and deserialize the value accordingly.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="7f284-121">下面的示例序列化一个名为 `Choices` 的类，其中包含两个字段，`MyChoice` 和 `ManyChoices`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7f284-121">The following example serializes a class named `Choices` that includes two fields, `MyChoice` and `ManyChoices`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7f284-122"><xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlChoiceIdentifierAttribute> 应用于指定（通过 <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlChoiceIdentifierAttribute.MemberName%2A> 属性）的每个字段，后者可获取或设置用于检测成员值的枚举。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7f284-122">The <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlChoiceIdentifierAttribute> is applied to each field that specifies (through the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlChoiceIdentifierAttribute.MemberName%2A> property) another class member that gets or sets an enumeration that detects the member value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7f284-123">`MyChoice` 字段可以设置为单个值，并在 `EnumType` 字段中找到相应的枚举成员。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7f284-123">The `MyChoice` field can be set to a single value, with a corresponding enumeration member found in the `EnumType` field.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7f284-124">`ManyChoices` 字段返回对象的数组。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7f284-124">The `ManyChoices` field returns an array of objects.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7f284-125">`ChoiceArray` 字段返回枚举值的数组。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7f284-125">The `ChoiceArray` field returns an array of enumeration values.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7f284-126">对于 "`ManyChoices`" 字段中的每个数组成员，都在 `ChoiceArray` 字段返回的数组中找到相应的成员。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7f284-126">For each array member in the `ManyChoices` field, a corresponding member is found in the array returned by the `ChoiceArray` field.</span></span>  
  
